text: Atlante F.C. is a Mexican professional football club. They play in Ascenso MX. The club is based in Cancún, Quintana Roo since 2007. ==Honours== ===Domestic championships=== *Mexican Primera División: 3 ::1946-47, 1992-93, Apertura 2007 ::Runner-up (4): 1945-46, 1949-50, 1950-51, 1981-82 *Segunda División de México: 2 ::1976-77, 1990-91 *National Amateur League: 2 ::1931-32, 1940-41 *Copa México: 3 ::1941-42, 1950-51, 1951-52 ::Runner-up (5): 1943-44, 1945-46, 1948-49, 1962-63, Clausura-2013 *Campeón de Campeones: 2 ::1941-42, 1951-52 ::Runner-up (2): 1946-47, 1950-51 ===International championships=== *CONCACAF Champions' Cup / CONCACAF Champions League: 2 ::1983, 2008-09 ::Runner-up (1): 1994 Category:Mexican football clubs Category:Quintana Roo Category:1916 establishments in Mexico
title: Atlante F.C.
